                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                                 Bug Eyes
                                 ========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43393,0)"}          43393,0




                         IMPORTANT!
                         ==========

